               <p>The 23d of April in the evening the prisoner came to me, and brought this watch to pawn for three guineas and a half, I stopped him.</p>
               <p>(The watch deposed to.)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I was going to Astley's, I was sitting down where they pay the money, and I picked up this watch, I kicked it with my boots.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17850629-56-verdict270" type="verdictDescription">
